SNES9X EMULATOR CORE (src/snes9x/)
================================================================================

The SNES emulation core is based on Snes9x, which has its own license that
restricts commercial use. The Snes9x license applies to all files under
src/snes9x/ and takes precedence over the GPL-3.0 for those files.

The full Snes9x license is reproduced below:

